reviews.review_text: All mediocre electric sets on the weekend shows here, all of which I was at. The best acoustic set is definitely the 11th !
10-10-1980 this is a Scarlet Fire to definitely check out...classic Dead interplay...beautifully measured transition into Fire...

a warm-up this a great scar fire.

sultry.  

jerry snakes his way into fire, letting the drums guide the transition.

but it's just a warm up to the big, rockin', super-tight astronomical night at THE FOX 11.30.80

if you like this scar>fire you MUST check out 11.30.80 -- 
it's the best. 

it's the difference between a nice glass of wine and owsley's finest.

nice aud. 
you can really feel the room.
